{"tid":1303241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 如何令TVB變成下一個亞視？","createTime":"2019-07-10T08:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T19:04:33.000Z","uid":158404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b30309cd93afd50de413a86532b09d8f43fa916c","tid":1303241,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:46:19.000Z","msg":"點樣可以系統化TVB杯葛行動？<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益，<br />\n<br />\n只有系統化先可以集合力量令TVB驚，<br />\n<br />\n正如遊行要正規地宣傳左出黎，先會召集到200萬人，<br />\n<br />\n尋晚有個好例子，用梁振英恥與為伍個招，每日post:<br />\n<br />\n全力支持TVB廣告商<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1300810\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1300810</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n其實就好似杯葛撐送中餐廳咁，<br />\n<br />\n到頭來都無完全系統化到令人可以杯葛，<br />\n<br />\n最易用我已經覺得係呢個，插入左google map:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1Jxy3dCPOA5VYlsX8Jcw48GryWxkwn9tj&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.31653180798728,114.15173855547414&amp;z=14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D1Jxy3dCPOA5VYlsX8Jcw48GryWxkwn9tj%26shorturl%3D1%26ll%3D22.31653180798728%2C114.15173855547414%26z%3D14&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=b2f330a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1Jxy3dCPOA5VYlsX8Jcw48GryWxkwn9tj&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.31653180798728,114.15173855547414&amp;z=14</a><br />\n<br />\n個邊可否出個app 或網頁，非常user friendly地令人揀到合適餐廳？<br />\n<br />\n大家天方夜譚下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n----------------<br />\n另外想成立個杯葛TVB TG group，<br />\n<br />\n比鍵盤戰士一齊做野，<br />\n<br />\n最主要就係系統化比有心人知要杯葛邊啲品牌，<br />\n<br />\n例如幫手每日做恥與為伍post，<br />\n<br />\n真係會出力嘅留低TG.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189e43cd40e3a0f462d9936acb22c78a7ee51e57","tid":1303241,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:49:28.000Z","msg":"就嚟連票都冇得投喇<br />\n<br />\n緊急! 反DQ! <br />\n用自己email send 意見書!!! <br />\n生產器出嘅不受理<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1302740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1302740</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"304888406682a62210e58683ebbd84dede2e94d3","tid":1303241,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JroBuGX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJroBuGX.png&h=99b7c355&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N8FkbVi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN8FkbVi.png&h=482e74b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4021eacae560fe9b6575cdbca36c60adca775263","tid":1303241,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:01:44.000Z","msg":"杯葛嘅TG group好似已經有？<br />\n尋日見到有個成千人 但冇join到<br />\n有無人可以share返個group出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外借po問如果我今晚繼續數廣告<br />\n應該舊po繼續定開新post？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6230dce1b329651479b5bd36b332a9ad92e580","tid":1303241,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4021eacae560fe9b6575cdbca36c60adca775263","tid":1303241,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:01:44.000Z","msg":"杯葛嘅TG group好似已經有？<br />\n尋日見到有個成千人 但冇join到<br />\n有無人可以share返個group出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外借po問如果我今晚繼續數廣告<br />\n應該舊po繼續定開新post？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:05:19.000Z","msg":"心穎姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n受小弟一拜<br />\n<br />\n應該開新？因為舊嘅睇唔到第一頁？每次個標題寫返個日日期？<br />\n小薯唔識"},{"pid":"dc195d01f903da1815f8b4a22620f686af550187","tid":1303241,"uid":32949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4021eacae560fe9b6575cdbca36c60adca775263","tid":1303241,"uid":75759,"like":0,"d